\"from\": 3372, \"to\": 3375}, {\"ngram\": \"the Dutch\", \"from\": 3381, \"to\": 3390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We knew out sprint was a lot better than the Americans.\", \"from\": 3392, \"to\": 3447, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sprint\", \"from\": 3404, \"to\": 3410}, {\"ngram\": \"the Americans\", \"from\": 3433, \"to\": 3446}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They might have a bit extra in an Olympic final, but we stayed in our boat and pushed on.\", \"from\": 3448, \"to\": 3537, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympic final\", \"from\": 3479, \"to\": 3495}, {\"ngram\": \"our boat\", \"from\": 3514, \"to\": 3522}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We tried to push early just to let them know that they were not getting a sniff... Doyle:I might have mitochondria in my right arm there!\", \"from\": 3538, \"to\": 3676, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sniff\", \"from\": 3610, \"to\": 3617}, {\"ngram\": \"mitochondria\", \"from\": 3640, \"to\": 3652}, {\"ngram\": \"my right arm\", \"from\": 3656, \"to\": 3668}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We had to go early.\", \"from\": 3677, \"to\": 3696, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We thought if we went like the Dutch did we would end up clearing the field, but the lads had a stormer so you can not take anything away from them.\", \"from\": 3697, \"to\": 3845, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Dutch\", \"from\": 3724, \"to\": 3733}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 3763, \"to\": 3772}, {\"ngram\": \"the lads\", \"from\": 3778, \"to\": 3786}, {\"ngram\": \"a stormer\", \"from\": 3791, \"to\": 3800}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 3821, \"to\": 3829}]}, {\"sentence\": \"First heavyweight medal ever (for Ireland), it's nice to write that into the history books.\", \"from\": 3847, \"to\": 3938, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3887, \"end\": 3894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.806829935166755, \"rank\": 0.14518895